Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Nakammaduka
185.
649Nakammapaccayā hetuyā satta, ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā satta, anantare satta, samanantare satta, sahajāte satta, aññamaññe satta, nissaye satta, upanissaye satta, purejāte satta, āsevane satta, āhāre satta, indriye satta, jhāne satta, magge satta, sampayutte satta, vippayutte satta, atthiyā satta, natthiyā satta, vigate satta, avigate satta.
